---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslations } from "../i18n/utils";

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const t = useTranslations(lang);
const title: string = t("nav.about")
---

<Layout title="MWL - Your local webagency">
  <Hero page=`${title}` />
  <main transition:animate="slide" class="text-white container mx-auto py-20 sm:py-52 text-xl px-8">
    <p><span class="mwl-yellow">MWL</span> consists of three seasoned developers, Darek, Jakob, and André.
      Our journey began at the heart of Umbraco HQ. 
      With a combined experience of over 10 years in working with Umbraco, we proudly introduce ourselves as certified Umbraco Masters and Azure Architects.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
      Darek, our DevOps maestro, ensures the seamless integration of development and operations, paving the way for efficient and reliable systems. 
      With a keen eye for optimization and a wealth of experience in managing the intricacies of deployment, Darek is the backbone of our technical infrastructure.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
      Meet Jakob, the coding virtuoso specializing in backend development. With a decade-long commitment to refining his craft, Jakob's expertise lies in creating robust and scalable solutions. 
      His in-depth knowledge of Umbraco and innovative approach to backend challenges make him an invaluable asset to our team.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
      Completing our trio is André, the artistic mind behind our frontend magic. 
      A frontend wizard with a passion for crafting user-centric and visually stunning interfaces, André brings a unique blend of creativity and technical finesse to every project. 
      His commitment to delivering seamless user experiences is evident in every line of code he writes. 
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
      At <span class="mwl-yellow">MWL</span>, our collaboration is not just about skills; it's about shared values, a commitment to excellence, and a passion for pushing the boundaries of what's possible. 
      With Umbraco as our canvas and Azure as our playground, we embark on a journey to turn your digital dreams into reality.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
      Join us as we navigate the ever-evolving landscape of web development, fueled by our deep-rooted Umbraco heritage and Azure expertise. 
      Whether you're envisioning a dynamic website, a powerful web application, or a custom-tailored solution, we have the skills and dedication to bring your ideas to life.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .mwl-yellow {
    color: var(--mwl-yellow-bright);
  }
</style>